

Agenda :

* Data binding
- Property binding
- Attribute binding
- class binding
- style binding
- event binding
* Angular directives 
- ngFor
- ngIf
- ngSwitch
- ngStyle
- ngClass

Property binding :bind the values of component or model properties to the HTML Element.

[property]='expression'


Angular directives :

- change behaviour / appearance / layout of the DOM element.

Types of directives

1.Structural - NgFor,NgIf,NgSwitch
2. Attribute - [ngClass] and [ngStyle]
3.Component - @Component